com.cycapservers.account

Class PlayerLBData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cycapservers.account.PlayerLBData

  • public class PlayerLBData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class calculates the ingame statistics for a player which are displayed on the leaderboard screen
